{"tid":994942,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"一隊波真係好需要佐真奴呢個球員","createTime":"2019-01-25T05:32:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T13:26:26.000Z","uid":107611,"like":52,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6ab1b1514095efae8b79b1021b6f5e4bfe0cb906","tid":994942,"uid":107611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T05:32:12.000Z","msg":"無論睇波或打FM FIFA就會發覺，<br />\n一個肯隨傳隨到走位到控緊球嘅對友附近，<br />\n接波後將個波快速傳送分邊俾隊友，<br />\n會令到隊波生好多!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n基本上你可以稱之為巴斯基斯同派路混合體，又難怪意大利都要搵佢入藉頂派路!<br />\n我唔排除第日巴塞又天價買佢返去頂巴斯基斯!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你可以認為佢冇咩明顯貢獻，但佢默默耕耘，犧牲自己接受外界批評先係車仔宜家踢到風生水起嘅主因!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔會話反佐真奴係球盲，但希望對佢有意見嘅人，學下佢踢法，對你無論踢波 定 出嚟做事會好有幫助!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08b2ee3eaa10bd7f2eb4cae87a616c32b7cceaef","tid":994942,"uid":198583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T05:33:17.000Z","msg":"我覺得冇哈登贏唔到"},{"pid":"c1427458072beb518afa64be3079f1db8193ad5a","tid":994942,"uid":77948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T05:33:24.000Z","msg":"啱 有佢𢭃住會放心好多"},{"pid":"c3188d1e9242d3656d8a9edd6a065a784d20b4b0","tid":994942,"uid":61271,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T05:34:31.000Z","msg":"想作潮文<br />\n<br />\n收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8caeece21ac4d2c3f2a2011afb9197dea89752cc","tid":994942,"uid":107611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3188d1e9242d3656d8a9edd6a065a784d20b4b0","tid":994942,"uid":61271,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T05:34:31.000Z","msg":"想作潮文<br />\n<br />\n收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T05:35:06.000Z","msg":"搵埋西書過檔組三巨頭就掂"},{"pid":"b5761fcd68f10686e2058